  "additional_info": "Also does the following (most users won't notice): \r\n\r\n-Replaces an image in favor of dynamic transparent color (RGBa) (faster browser loading/rendering). \r\n\r\n-Pushes down Battlelog's main header to leave room at the top so the user header doesn't overlap.\r\n\r\n-Written for the /r/battlefield3 community.",
  "style_tags": [],
  "css": "@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);\r\n\r\n@-moz-document domain(\"battlelog.battlefield.com\") {\r\n    #base-mainheader-container{\r\n        position: fixed !important;\r\n        background: rgba(0,0,0,/*[[settingplaceholder]]*/) !important;\r\n        border-bottom: rgba(255,255,255,.2) 1px solid !important;\r\n    }\r\n    #base-submainheader{\r\n        top: 64px;\r\n    }\r\n    #base-bf3-body #content{\r\n        padding: 64px 0 0 0 !important;\r\n    }\r\n}",
